text = "Scavenger Log [pause=0.5]- Unified timedate: 103022.12 [pause]
I made it out.[pause=0.5].[pause=0.5].[pause=0.5] barely.[pause]

The machine kept resisting the attempts to open the doors, overriding the commands[pause]. At first I just thought it was old, dysfunctional security systems…[pause] But then it started to seem…[pause] Intentional??[pause]

Whatever it was.. I couldn't look back. [pause]I wasn’t about to stay trapped in that tin-can…[pause]

A machine is just a machine… No real thoughts, no real feelings... Just metal...[pause] Nothing more.[pause=2]

And yet...[pause] I can't shake the feeling there was more to this frigate…. [pause] Why do I feel guilty for just leaving….?
[pause]"
